The Ugly 5 Night Race Series, presented by the Middelburg Marathon Club, will be launching this Wednesday evening, with the first of its five races beginning at Hoërskool Kanonkop. Here’s what you need to know: • The race will start at 18:30 this Wednesday evening. • An R80 entry fee for the 10km, and a R40 entry fee for the 4.9km is payable. Alternatively, a once-off payment for the whole series can be made at the following rates: R300 for the 10km and R150 for the 4.9km. • The other races will take place on March 29; April 12; September 20; and November 23.